PrecisTransfer to the Canada Post Corporation of the title to four real properties situate at various locations in Ontario and Manitoba, in exchange for the transfer to Her Majesty of the title to a property situate at 1495 Heron Road, in the City of Ottawa, Ontario, known as Pavillion "M". . PROPERTIES to be acquired by the Canada Post Corporation: . 1. 2435/2439 Eglinton Avenue East, Scarborough, Ontario (vacant land) 2. Post Office, 139 Main Street, Ailsa Craig, Ontario 3. Post Office, Bay Street, Baysville, Ontario 4. Post Office Tower, 266 Graham Avenue, Winnipeg, Manitoba .
